*quantlib-0.3.12 (22 Apr 2006)

  22 Apr 2006; Marcelo Goes <vanquirius@gentoo.org> +quantlib-0.3.12.ebuild:
  0.3.12 version bump.

  19 Feb 2006; Joshua Kinard <kumba@gentoo.org> quantlib-0.3.0.ebuild:
  Removing mips keyword as we have no way to test this package and unstable
  keyword was added w/o our notification so long ago. If package becomes used
  on mips, drop us a note/bug.

  05 Feb 2006; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> quantlib-0.3.10.ebuild:
  Mark 0.3.10 stable on alpha

  24 Dec 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  quantlib-0.3.10.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

